These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, palaceing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, begonia, iris
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, canasta, chess
House: victorian, palace, art-deco, cottage
1. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the palace house##1
3. the person playing canasta is the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who's hobby is palaceing is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is the victorian house##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the art-deco house##1
9. the person who's hobby is palaceing is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | palaceing  | camping | card-games |
| Flower           | daisy | amaryllis | iris  | begonia  |
| Game   | chess       | canasta      | bridge | billiard      |
| House           | victorian          | palace     | art-deco    | cottage     |

