.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, software-developer, police-officer, photographer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, balloon-flower, lily
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, martial-arts, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the designer##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the police-officer is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the software-developer##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the designer##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Job      | police-officer     | designer       | software-developer | photographer        |
| Flower          | lily     | orchid       | balloon-flower   | daffodil   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | adventure       | spy     | drama    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

