.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, kale, nectarine, broccoli
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo, aristoff, oliveros
City: rome, hamburg, edinburgh, colone
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony
 1. the person eating broccoli is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the person eating nectarine is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Food      | kale | strawberry       | broccoli        | nectarine        |
| Cigar           | montecristo   | aristoff | cain   | oliveros |
| City   | rome     | hamburg    | colone | edinburgh        |
| Pet           | mouse         | hedgehog  | pony       | lizard         |

