.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, domino, scrabble, poker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, soccer, parkour
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, lilac, ebony, brown
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing domino##1
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Game           | domino   | monopoly  | poker | scrabble |
| Sport   | soccer | parkour       | cricket       | surfing     |
| Color   | ebony       | brown    | lilac     | azure  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

