.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, orchid, lily, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, january, july
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, metal, hip-hop, country
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the fan of country##1
6. the fan of country is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Flower           | daisy  | lily    | orchid | bellflower |
| Birthday   | january      | june    | march         | july    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Music-Genre         | metal | techno | country      | hip-hop      |

