.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, car, bike
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, dancer, doctor, writer
House: gothic-revival, modern, art-deco, townhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, baking, traveling, puzzles
 1. the person driving the car is the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the person driving the bus is the modern house##1
 3. the accountant is the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the bus##1
 5. the art-deco house is the writer##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | bus  | bike | car     | quad-bike |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| House   | modern | art-deco  | gothic-revival    | townhouse  |
| Hobby           | traveling   | puzzles       | dancing       | baking      |

