 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the fan of funk is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre    | spy | documentary     | time-travel    | romance |
