.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, milk, water
House: craftsman, wooden, cape-cod, cottage
There 4 different types of food: apricot, lime, carrot, papaya
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, horse, dog
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
2. the person drinking water is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
7. the wooden house is the owner of the frog##1
8. the owner of the horse is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the owner of the dog is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | water      | 7up         | milk        | juice      |
| House           | wooden | craftsman | cape-cod  | cottage  |
| Food   | carrot    | apricot     | lime | papaya     |
| Pet     | frog        | horse     | hedgehog     | dog |

